Package: sspLNIRT
Title: Sample Size Planning for Item Calibration using the Joint Hierarchical Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Data: 2026
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sebastian A. J.",
           family = "Lortz",
           email = "s.a.j.lortz@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Sample size planning tools for the Joint Hierarchical Model 
    using a 2-PL normal ogive model for response accuracy and a 3-PL 
    log-normal model for response time, estimated via the LNIRT package.
